{"tid":2371894,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"受大陸資本帶動 主板成交破3千億元史上最高 港股高收779點","createTime":"2021-01-19T08:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T08:24:05.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1939b230904952a0b08c5f29911b86ba5b7f521e","tid":2371894,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T08:22:48.000Z","msg":"港股高收779點 主板成交破3千億元史上最高<br />\n<br />\n港股連升4個交易日，早段創逾1年半新高，恒生指數高見29848點，最多曾升986點，午後升幅一度收窄，收市報29642點，升779點，升幅2.7%<br />\n<br />\n全日主板成交額近3016億元，是史上最高成交額，受到於北水持續流入帶動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571212-20210119.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571212-20210119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=60378ab9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571212-20210119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6ce8900a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571212-20210119.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6ff9e1da2ef75b9863f8f36d97a954c52c565ad8","tid":2371894,"uid":21634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T08:24:05.000Z","msg":"夠鐘走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}